{"title": "Tranquil Terrain with mae", "slug": "tranquil-terrain-with-mae", "date": "2024-11-25", "author": "theline1", "excerpt": "Mae is an artist known for her minimalistic and romantic approach to landscape art, blending realism and surrealism. Since joining the cryptoart scene in 2021, she has created \"Postcards by Mae,\" a digital collection reflecting her artistic journey, featuring tranquil landscapes that evoke a sense of nostalgia and peace.", "categories": ["Illustration", "illustration", "Landscape", "mintface collection", "noble gallery"], "featuredImage": "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/postcards-with-mae-001.png", "images": ["https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection-1024x982.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection-1320x1266.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-2048x1536.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-600x384.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection-600x575.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-300x192.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-600x450.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection-300x288.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-300x225.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-1320x990.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-1024x768.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection-768x736.png", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-1320x845.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-1024x655.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-768x492.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-768x576.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-1536x1152.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-400x300.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-1536x983.jpg", "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-2048x1311.jpg"], "content": "<h2>The Artist: mae</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Mae's work explores a minimal and romantic approach to landscape art with a touch of surrealism. Joining the cryptoart movement in 2021, mae has brought the timeline peace and tranquility. The destinations may be a work of fiction, but the colorwork is derived from photographs she has taken throughout her life. There is a familiarity to the landscapes, as if we are remembering a time when our forefathers arrived at the frontier for the first time and experienced its immense beauty.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-300x225.jpg 300w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-768x576.jpg 768w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-400x300.jpg 400w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-1320x990.jpg 1320w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/notus-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>notus by mae</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"lines - especially soft, flowing lines - create a biological response in us. they are calming, and they put us at ease.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>mae</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: \"Postcards by Mae\"</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Postcards by Mae is a unique collection that serves as Enixsta's love letter to the art community. This project comprises a series of digital postcards, each featuring distinctive artwork that reflects the artist's personal experiences and artistic journey. Postcards made it possible for anyone to collect mae's work with 1,833 editions sold. Her signature objects are presented with clarity across the collection; manicured hedges, undulating lined hills, crisp leaves, reflective depths and the bright ethereal beauty of a new day.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"718\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection-1024x982.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection-1024x982.png 1024w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection-300x288.png 300w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection-768x736.png 768w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection-1320x1266.png 1320w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection-600x575.png 600w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/tranquil-terrain-postcards-with-mae-collection.png 1508w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>postcards collection by mae</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: \"Seussian #46\"\n</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The Seussian collection elevates the undulating hills into ribbons of fantasy. The layers of history bedded down over time leaving only the land and its watery surroundings. The sense of escapism mae's work provides the viewer, gives a visual evocation of the immense peace that comes with free flowing life.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"479\" src=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-1024x655.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-1024x655.jpg 1024w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-300x192.jpg 300w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-768x492.jpg 768w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-1536x983.jpg 1536w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-2048x1311.jpg 2048w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-1320x845.jpg 1320w, https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Seussian46-by-mae-600x384.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Seussian #46 by mae</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/mae/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tmae | Line 170\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>"}